{"word":"H1516 - גַּיְא - gayʼ - gah'-ee - Valley","slug":"H1516","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גַּיְא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gayʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gah'-ee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Valley"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D9;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D9;&#x05D0; - gay'  gay</b> - <i>gah'ee, gah'ee</i><p/>Probably (by transmutation) from the same root as <a href=\"#/H1466\">H1466</a> (abbreviated); a <i>gorge</i> (from its <i>lofty</i> sides; hence narrow, but not a gully or winter torrent): - valley."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1515\">H1515</a>, <a href=\"#/H1522\">H1522</a>"}]}